               Confined Six Weeks
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>SIMPSON - <rs id="t18291029-196-verdict1107" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18291029-196-verdict1107" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
